						               													<description>Dark Files: 01-KOMA is a multimedia detective game experience in a realistic criminal case.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Detectives work together to solve a case with the help of the information provided in different ways: Some information is provided by the printed media within the game (like newspapers, photos, business cards, letters etc.), another part of the information is provided digitally (on websites, by phone calls or SMS). Therefore the following tools are necessary to play the game: mobile phone and internet browser.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What happened to Ben? - You find your friend Ben (39) knocked out and unconscious in his kitchen. After taking the necessary steps to help him, you wonder what could have happened. As a friend and close confidant, you dive into Ben's life and try to find out with your mutual acquaintance Larissa why Ben fell victim to this crime. And what does his current case have to do with it?&amp;#10;A gripping and multidimensional TRUE CRIME detective game experience.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Koma is the 1st case of the dark files detective game series. Each case is self-contained. Dive into the exciting world of detective games. Solve puzzles, crack codes, examine documents, combine evidence and facts, draw conclusions and solve the case!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
